name: Research Specialization: Thesis
description: An individual thesis done under the direction of a faculty member. Lecture and seminar presentations of proposals in the Fall session. Enrolment is restricted to PSY Research Specialists. Not eligible for CR/NCR option.
prerequisites: Enrolment in the PSY Research Specialist program, PSY309H1, and one of PSY319H1/PSY329H1/PSY339H1/PSY359H1/PSY369H1/PSY379H1/PSY389H1
